Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when it was
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.15,0:00:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that your laughing voice grew far away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The end comes all too quickly
