Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to bring back your smile
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.73,0:01:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times, I won’t stop singing
